  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the effect of probiotics in childhood recurrent
      abdominal pain. Patients will be randomly assigned to receive L. reuteri or placebo for 4
      weeks with a follow up phase of additional 4 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prospective randomized double-blind placebo-controlled trial.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
